<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>[TLG]</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

        <section id="project-page">
            <p id="heading">
                Below are some of the projects i'm working on or have worked on, more on my <a href="https://github.com/thelocalgodd" target="_blank">GitHub.</a>
            </p>

            <div id="project-text-boxes">
				<a href="https://github.com/thelocalgodd/folio_astro">
					<TextBox 
					heading="thelocalgodd.me 2.0"
					content=`
						I'm redesigning and rebuilding my personal portfolio from scratch, taking inspiration from a couple of websites I have seen.
					`
					/>
				</a>
				
				<a href="https://github.com/thelocalgodd/tailwind-auto-script">
					<TextBox 
					heading="tailwind-auto-script"
					content=`
					this is a basic bash script I wrote to automate the process of creating a new react project with vite, adding tailwind to it, and configuring it to work.
					`
					/>
				</a>
				
				<a href="https://github.com/thelocalgodd/simp-calc">
					<TextBox 
						heading="basic calculator app"
						content=`
							exactly what the name suggests, it is a basic calculator app with super basic functionalities, I made it just for practice sake.
						`
					/>
				</a>
            </div>

            <p id="more-projects">
                check out more projects 
                <a href="https://github.com/thelocalgodd">
                    <b>
                        here
                    </b>
                </a>
            </p>

        </section>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
